OL,3,CJersey's Consumer Council calls for
OL,4,Cutility regulator for island
OL,6,FThe Jersey Consumer Council is calling
OL,7,Fon the island's government to
OL,8,Fintroduce a regulator on the island to
OL,9,Fensure prices for utilities are fair.
OL,11,FIt comes as Islands Energy is set to
OL,12,Fincrease gas prices by 7.5% from
OL,13,FMonday (13 January). The increase
OL,14,Fmeans the price per unit is now 28.18p
OL,15,Fresulting in an average increase of
OL,16,F#114 a year.
