OL,3,CJersey's Consumer Council calls for
OL,4,Cutility regulator for island
OL,6,FMeanwhile customers in the Isle of
OL,7,FMan, which Islands Energy also run gas
OL,8,Fservices for, are seeing their bills
OL,9,Freduce by 13.8%. The unit price is now
OL,10,F9.76p which means the average
OL,11,Fhousehold bill is being cut by around
OL,12,F#156 a year.
OL,14,FGas prices in Guernsey increased by
OL,15,F10% at the beginning of the year but
OL,16,Fis still lower than Jersey.
