OL,3,CJersey's Consumer Council calls for
OL,4,Cutility regulator for island
OL,6,FHe adds: "This is why, as a consumer
OL,7,Fcouncil, we are calling for a
OL,8,Fregulator who will give independent
OL,9,Foversight of all of our utility
OL,10,Findustries.
OL,12,F"To make sure their prices have been
OL,13,Fchallenged, to make sure there is
OL,14,Ftransparency for the customers and to
OL,15,Fmake sure there is protection for
OL,16,Fconsumers when things go wrong."
