OL,3,CJersey's Consumer Council calls for
OL,4,Cutility regulator for island
OL,6,FHowever it's not just residential
OL,7,Fhomes about to experience a hike in
OL,8,Fthe price of gas. Entwhistles Fish &
OL,9,FChips is the only business of its kind
OL,10,Fin the east of the island and needs
OL,11,Fgas to operate.
OL,13,FWith the rise in utility prices, they
OL,14,Fmay be forced to close for good when
OL,15,Ftheir lease runs out in two years.
