OL,3,CJersey's Consumer Council calls for
OL,4,Cutility regulator for island
OL,6,FJon De Gruchy is the owner and says:
OL,7,F"It's not worth the stress and
OL,8,Fheartache, the hard work. My wife now
OL,9,Fworks so hard now, more than she's
OL,10,Fever done, same with myself. We do
OL,11,Fmore hours now than we've ever done
OL,12,Ffor little or no money at all, we make
OL,13,Fno profit anymore, it's gone."
OL,15,F"It's very unfair. Very, very unfair.
OL,16,FAs if it's not hard enough, that is
OL,17,Fgoing to add another #1000 on top of
OL,18,Four yearly bill straightaway. That's
OL,19,Ftoo much. It's starting to get silly."
