OL,3,CJersey's Consumer Council calls for
OL,4,Cutility regulator for island
OL,6,FIn response, Island Energy provided
OL,7,Fthis statement: "Island Energy has
OL,8,Falways sought to protect its customers
OL,9,Ffrom the volatility of gas prices
OL,10,Fprompted by global events.
OL,12,F"Jersey and the Isle of Man have
OL,13,Fsignificantly different gas markets
OL,14,Fand costs to operate therefore it is
OL,15,Fnot appropriate to compare the two.
OL,17,F"The recent price rises enable us to
OL,18,Ffurther invest in the network and
OL,19,Fdeliver for our customers."
